Jefferson!

1659
02:25:30.846 --> 02:25:32.097
Come on, start.

1660
02:25:33.432 --> 02:25:36.560
It won't start! It won't start!
The bastard won't start!

1661
02:25:49.114 --> 02:25:50.574
