in the line of duty.

1679
02:28:20.224 --> 02:28:21.725
You did a fine job, major.

1680
02:28:24.478 --> 02:28:25.729
I'll see you around.

1681
02:28:26.397 --> 02:28:28.524
You did a good job, soldier.

1682
02:28:28.690 --> 02:28:31.485
